				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am equipped roughly in elemental gear. My opponent cleric was equipped roughly in elemental gear.
<br />

<br />
1. Sic pet.
<br />
2. Dump HoE on him/her as fast as possible
<br />
3. Dispell twice while he/she is dealing with HoE
<br />
4. Debuff while she's dealing with HoE
<br />
5. Pop off a nuke or two
<br />
6. If the pet's rooted, get rid of it and bring one out of suspend
<br />
7. Always pick a dueling location where you can abuse the territory.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=304991" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Qaedain Magi'kot</a></span>
<br />
<i>The Company - Bertoxx</i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
