				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I find no problems beating clerics, just takes hell of long time with there heals.
<br />

<br />
The cleric pet hammer should be no problem if you have your DS up, they die pretty fast.
<br />

<br />
Don't know what your MR or anything is like but if it's decent should be able to resits stuns and even nukes most of the time. 
<br />

<br />
Keep the pet on him/her that will determine it, if he roots pet, just annul pet, need to keep it on him/her to keep bashing/stunning heals.
<br />

<br />
Keep ds up if cleric decides to meele, nuke the cleric down.
<br />

<br />
send in aa pets if you have them, dispell once or twice, debuff, keep pet on him, nuke down...should work unless he just totally outgears you<br />_________________<br />Matalus
<br />
Matalus
